{"tid":737764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"迎戰Steam攻中國市場　騰訊將推國際版WeGame","createTime":"2018-07-11T05:15:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T16:53:37.000Z","uid":77196,"like":3,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"4ba5905d0fbd6e4a9576d6723798dbb8196d59c2","tid":737764,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T05:15:29.000Z","msg":"作為網遊及手遊王者騰訊控股(0700)，為了應對來自另一個遊戲平台Steam有意進軍內地市場的挑戰，決定推出WeGame國際版，以鞏固其王者地位。據《南華早報》報道，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>騰訊將會在香港推出WeGame海外版</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述騰訊深圳發言人早前指出，香港版WeGame目前正在開發，又指出該版本適用於海外玩家，透過有關平台將更多內地遊戲帶到全球市場。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>據了解在香港推出WeGame可以避過內地審查制度，滿足國際玩家</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n業內人士指WeGame目前遊戲數目較少<br />\n<br />\nWeGame是騰訊在去年9月推出的內地上線遊戲平台，透過有關平台，現家可以購買﹑下載遊戲，同時WeGame亦具備直播及社區等功能。有業內人士指出，目前WeGame只有200款產品，作為全球開放平台而言產品數目較少。"},{"pid":"2d9e55724611585b9ad2e347dbc226a59e462417","tid":737764,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T05:27:52.000Z","msg":"in 0700 we trust"},{"pid":"11ab5dd18b15aa66762b9391078295b300de7839","tid":737764,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T05:31:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c0e06551bbe82e2c20b72ab49c03bd8e5f10a2","tid":737764,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T05:48:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c2fb72506da31966f1a49d657c10c0af73d1df3","tid":737764,"uid":34010,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T06:18:39.000Z","msg":"支持！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nsteam 批支那狗快d 過主啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea8739deff7222a186bcf4acf3afecfeadd464b","tid":737764,"uid":114754,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"3c2fb72506da31966f1a49d657c10c0af73d1df3","tid":73776